JDK ⊃ JRE ⊃ JVM

👉 matlab:

JDK sabse bada
uske andar JRE
uske andar JVM

⚙️ 1. JVM (Java Virtual Machine)
👉 Kya hai?

JVM ek engine hai jo Java bytecode ko run karta hai

.java → compile → .class (bytecode) → JVM → machine code

🧠 Simple language

JVM = “translator + executor”

🔥 Responsibilities
Bytecode ko run karna
Memory manage karna (Heap, Stack)
Garbage Collection
Platform independence

💡 Important line (interview me bolna)

“JVM makes Java platform independent by converting bytecode to machine-specific instructions.”

⚙️ 2. JRE (Java Runtime Environment)
👉 Kya hai?

JRE = JVM + libraries

JRE = JVM + runtime libraries + supporting files

🧠 Simple

“Program run karne ke liye jo chahiye — wo sab JRE me hota hai”

❗ Important

👉 JRE me compiler nahi hota

👉 tum Java program run kar sakte ho, but bana nahi sakte

⚙️ 3. JDK (Java Development Kit)
👉 Kya hai?

JDK = JRE + development tools

JDK = JRE + compiler + debugger + tools

🔧 Tools inside JDK
javac → compile
java → run
jdb → debugger
🧠 Simple

“Java develop + run dono karna hai → JDK chahiye”

🎯 Real Flow (IMPORTANT)
1. Write code → Hello.java
2. Compile → javac Hello.java
3. Bytecode → Hello.class
4. Run → java Hello
5. JVM executes it

🔥 Super Simple Analogy

| Component | Analogy                          |
| --------- | -------------------------------- |
| JVM       | Engine                           |
| JRE       | Car (engine + fuel + system)     |
| JDK       | Car factory (tools to build car) |

❓ Q1: JVM platform dependent hai ya independent?

👉 Answer:

JVM itself = platform dependent (Windows JVM, Mac JVM alag hota hai)
Java = platform independent

🔥 trick yahin hota hai

❓ Q2: Kya hum JRE ke bina Java program run kar sakte hain?

👉 ❌ Nahi

👉 JVM + libraries chahiye → JRE

❓ Q3: Kya JDK ke bina Java run ho sakta hai?

👉 ✔️ Haan
👉 agar JRE installed hai

❓ Q4: .class file me kya hota hai?

👉 Bytecode (machine independent code)

❓ Q5: JVM ka part hai ya JRE ka?

👉 JVM JRE ka part hai

❓ Q6: Agar system me sirf JDK hai, kya JRE alag install karna padega?

👉 ❌ Nahi
👉 JDK me already JRE included hota hai

❓ Q7: Java platform independent kaise hai?

👉 Bytecode + JVM

❓ Q8: Kya JVM directly .java file run karta hai?

👉 ❌ Nahi
👉 pehle compile → .class

❓ Q9: Heap aur Stack kis part ka hai?

👉 JVM memory

❓ Q9: Heap aur Stack kis part ka hai?

👉 JVM memory

❓ Q10: Garbage Collection kaun karta hai?

👉 JVM

🚀 Final One-Line Summary
JVM → runs bytecode
JRE → provides runtime environment
JDK → provides tools to develop + run
